pageTitle: High School Sports | Sept. 18 2009 football Park City-Manti | Deseret News
textBeforeTable: Rushing Individual stats Miners blow past Manti Related The Miners jumped out to a 21-0 lead after the first quarter as Dylan Chynoweth had three TD runs, including a 79-yard jog. Chynoweth rushed 15 times for 241 yards while Erik Walker had one carry for 29 yards and a score. Matt Christensen rushed four times for 34 yards and two touchdowns while Andy Proctor had seven carries for 96 yards and a TD. The Miners had 500 yards of offense, 403 yards through the air.
